{"tid":1360657,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不只要香港獨立，我哋要廣州獨立","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T00:22:33.000Z","uid":258731,"like":25,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a2ed48a62111ec374f48a63216842f4e5c8d2d","tid":1360657,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180312/large/1520845068_c535.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180312%2Flarge%2F1520845068_c535.png&h=a6811387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/independence-03122018090537.html/independence.jpg/@@images/15d3acff-5473-4cfd-a046-4a22bbe3293c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Findependence-03122018090537.html%2Findependence.jpg%2F%40%40images%2F15d3acff-5473-4cfd-a046-4a22bbe3293c.jpeg&h=3af6f390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Guangdong_in_China_%28%2Ball_claims_hatched%29.svg/300px-Guangdong_in_China_%28%2Ball_claims_hatched%29.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fe3%2FGuangdong_in_China_%2528%252Ball_claims_hatched%2529.svg%2F300px-Guangdong_in_China_%2528%252Ball_claims_hatched%2529.svg.png&h=43613fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係香港獨立，地理基礎唔夠大，容易被老解圍攻<br />\n但係如果成個廣東省獨立，成為一個獨立國家，對於中共威脅會更大<br />\n<br />\n比起純粹香港獨立好處<br />\n1：人口更多，能推動更繁榮經濟<br />\n2：國界將會更廣闊，比較能抵禦外敵（共產黨）入侵<br />\n3：農業，製造產業比香港成熟，地理資源更多<br />\n     <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 變相香港無需再憂慮食水，食物不足問題</span></span><br />\n     糧食短缺、糧價高脤、水資源問題不攻自破<br />\n4：廣東省佔全中國地理面積十分之一，廣州帶頭獨立，中共猶如大出血，割咗一大忽肉，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中共滅亡指日可待</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n語言<br />\n廣東省其中一主要語言為廣東話，與香港共通。廣東話，省內又通稱廣府話、廣州話、白話，是廣東省內影響力最大、使用人口最多的地方語言，省內使用的人口近<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4000萬人</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n政治<br />\n作為近代革命發源地，廣州自中華民國時代就是中國社會運動的中心。每次全國性社會運動都有廣州民眾的響應和參與。以廣州為中心的大規模的社會運動，最早有1925年至1926年在廣州和香港同時舉辦的省港大罷工。<br />\n<br />\n廣州市民在1989年更發起活動聲援天安門民主運動，百萬人聚集海珠廣場圍繞廣州解放紀念碑集會。初期廣州傳媒以「愛國運動」名義支持。6月4日發生六四事件，解放軍在北京天安門廣場清場，屠殺學生和市民，廣州爆發大遊行、罷工、罷市，交通癱瘓，持續至第二日。<br />\n<br />\n2010年7月逾千市民在地鐵江南西站出口聚集舉行<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2010年廣州撐粵語行動請願活動</span></span>，為廣府文化發出自己的呼聲。事後中國大陸傳媒封鎖消息，廣州亦屏蔽香港電視相關的新聞片段。<br />\n<br />\n唯一香港要努力係要重新建立粵族身份認同<br />\n或可由香港輸出粵族秩序"},{"pid":"ea1756f743b72119df79d008e1540cd248bb8769","tid":1360657,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e646ecafa2ac1ff2b0ce35646e014ebc433783f8","tid":1360657,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"支那咁多鏡頭都敢寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a83b1a1c9c9770abe0481f20d8a61d6c459a2dc","tid":1360657,"uid":157516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:18:19.000Z","msg":"好，識得啲廣州人其實都好認同我地"},{"pid":"697beed087dac5df267dc67b9d48df133d3ccb4a","tid":1360657,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:19:16.000Z","msg":"港區城邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e6223b5c560005bc8e0bb8b05ec0a204a42a31","tid":1360657,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:19:48.000Z","msg":"應該係「兩廣獨立」<br />\n歷史上有過"},{"pid":"dc3e1871c35acc2663777064f90fd2fc18f7507d","tid":1360657,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:20:14.000Z","msg":"真。大灣區？"},{"pid":"ead08cce1fffab79a75c481c25caad20d873ac40","tid":1360657,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:20:4